description.plain:
Makonnen Kamali Sheran (born April 12, 1989), popularly known as iLoveMakonnen, is an American recording artist from South Los Angeles, CA.

Makonnen ran a blog interviewing recording artists, such as Lil B and Soulja Boy in 2008. At the same time, he began his music career, influenced by his grandmother, who was an opera singer, by releasing tracks on MySpace. In Atlanta, Makonnen met producer Mike WiLL Made-It in 2012, who introduced him to local producers such as Metro Boomin and Sonny Digital. After releasing his second EP, his song “Club Goin' Up on a Tuesday,” produced by Metro and Sonny Digital, gained Drake’s attention, who contacted Sonny Digital and jumped on a remix with the title renamed to “Tuesday.” Makonnen signed to OVO Sound a few weeks later. On April 19, 2016, it was confirmed that he had been dropped from the label before releasing an album under them.

Makonnen Kamali Sheran (born April 12, 1989), popularly known as iLoveMakonnen, is an American recording artist from South Los Angeles, CA.

Makonnen ran a blog interviewing recording artists, such as Lil B and Soulja Boy in 2008. At the same time, he began his music career, influenced by his grandmother, who was an opera singer, by releasing tracks on MySpace. In Atlanta, Makonnen met producer Mike WiLL Made-It in 2012, who introduced him to local producers such as Metro Boomin and Sonny Digital. After releasing his second EP, his song “Club Goin' Up on a Tuesday,” produced by Metro and Sonny Digital, gained Drake’s attention, who contacted Sonny Digital and jumped on a remix with the title renamed to “Tuesday.” Makonnen signed to OVO Sound a few weeks later. On April 19, 2016, it was confirmed that he had been dropped from the label before releasing an album under them.

description.plain:
Drake jumps on I LOVE MAKONNEN’s popular underground hit “Club Goin' up on a Tuesday”. The song appears as the third track on the re-release of the ILoveMakonnen EP. Critically acclaimed, the song garnered a Best Rap/Sung Collaboration Grammy nomination, along with being certified platinum.

Just hours after showing some love via Instagram, Drizzy Drake decides to come through and share his new verse.

http://vimeo.com/109541524

description.plain:
Makonnen has to work on the weekends due to his drug dealing habits, so Tuesday is the only night he has to let loose and have fun. Clubs are typically abandoned on Tuesday nights, but Makonnen still has the club goin' up.

This song was highly popularized by Drake’s remix, which made the Billboard Hot 100 list. Eventually, Drake signed Makonnen to his label, October’s Very Own.
